OL,3,CTech companies not doing enough to
OL,4,Cstop phone theft, say MPs
OL,6,FTech companies are not doing enough to
OL,7,Fcombat mobile phone theft, MPs have
OL,8,Fsaid as they urged the Home Secretary
OL,9,Fto take a "robust stance" on the issue.
OL,11,FIn a letter to Shabana Mahmood, the
OL,12,FCommons Science, Innovation and
OL,13,FTechnology Committee expressed concern
OL,14,Fthat companies including Apple,
OL,15,FSamsung and Google were not
OL,16,Fimplementing technical measures that
OL,17,Fcould "design out" phone theft.
