OL,3,CTech companies not doing enough to
OL,4,Cstop phone theft, say MPs
OL,6,FThe committee said it had pressed the
OL,7,Fcompanies on why they had not
OL,8,Fimplemented steps to prevent stolen
OL,9,Fhandsets connecting to cloud accounts
OL,10,Fin foreign countries.
OL,12,FSuch moves would make stolen handsets
OL,13,Fmuch less valuable if shipped overseas.
OL,15,FThe MPs also expressed scepticism at
OL,16,Fcompanies' claims in written evidence
OL,17,Fto the committee that phones were
OL,18,Fmainly being sold for parts, pointing
OL,19,Fto figures from the Metropolitan
OL,20,FPolice that 78% of stolen devices were
OL,21,Flater connected to overseas networks.
