OL,3,CTech companies not doing enough to
OL,4,Cstop phone theft, say MPs
OL,6,FThey said: "Their repeated pivots to
OL,7,Fanswering questions about data
OL,8,Fsecurity rather than devices, and
OL,9,Finsistence that the phones were broken
OL,10,Fdown and sold for parts, without any
OL,11,Fevidence to support this assertion,
OL,12,Fwas telling."
OL,14,FIn evidence to the committee, Apple
OL,15,Fsaid it was considering measures to
OL,16,Fallow for remote blocking of stolen
OL,17,Fdevices, but had "concerns with this
OL,18,Fapproach if wider privacy and security
OL,19,Fimplications are not sufficiently
OL,20,Fconsidered", adding there was no
OL,21,F"silver bullet" to preventing theft.
