OL,3,CTech companies not doing enough to
OL,4,Cstop phone theft, say MPs
OL,6,FGoogle insisted its existing
OL,7,Fprotections offered a "robust
OL,8,Fsolution", while Samsung told the
OL,9,Fcommittee it made "significant
OL,10,Fcontributions" to device security
OL,11,Fthrough its research.
OL,13,FPhone theft has become an increasing
OL,14,Fconcern in recent years, especially in
OL,15,FLondon where around 80,000 handsets
OL,16,Fwere stolen last year, according to
OL,17,Fthe Metropolitan Police.
