OL,3,CTech companies not doing enough to
OL,4,Cstop phone theft, say MPs
OL,6,FMany of the devices end up being
OL,7,Fshipped overseas, with the Met
OL,8,Falleging earlier in October that one
OL,9,Fsmuggling network had sent up to
OL,10,F40,000 stolen phones from the UK to
OL,11,FChina in the past year.
OL,13,FThe MPs told the Home Secretary they
OL,14,Fwould "support a robust stance on this
OL,15,Fissue from the Government" and urged
OL,16,Fher to convene a phone theft summit
OL,17,Fwith tech companies and the police.
