OL,3,CTech companies not doing enough to
OL,4,Cstop phone theft, say MPs
OL,6,FMinisters held such a summit in
OL,7,FFebruary 2025 but a follow-up meeting
OL,8,Fplanned for May this year did not take
OL,9,Fplace.
OL,11,FCommittee chairwoman Dame Chi Onwurah
OL,12,Fsaid: "Given the exploding growth of
OL,13,Fphone theft, it's clear existing
OL,14,Fdeterrents from tech companies are not
OL,15,Fworking.
OL,17,F"To protect the public's property,
OL,18,Fwellbeing and privacy, the Government
OL,19,Fmust take a strong stance and hold the
OL,20,Flong-delayed follow-up phone theft
OL,21,Fsummit.
